       S0000-MAIN-RTN.

      *@1 초기화
           PERFORM  S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN
              THRU  S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT

      *@1 입력값 CHECK(SYSIN)
           PERFORM  S2000-VALIDATION-RTN
              THRU  S2000-VALIDATION-EXT

      *@1  SYSIN GET MOVE
           PERFORM  S3000-SYSDATA-MOVE-RTN
              THRU  S3000-SYSDATA-MOVE-EXT

           IF  WK-H-I-GUBUN-CD = CO-CHA-1
           THEN
      *#1 삭제구분이 1(전체삭제)인 경우
      *@1 카드고객수신기본(THKJL0021) 전체삭제
               PERFORM  S3000-KJL0021-ALL-DELETE-RTN
                  THRU  S3000-KJL0021-ALL-DELETE-EXT
           ELSE
      *#1 삭제구분이 1(전체삭제)이 아닌경우
      *@1 카드고객수신기본(THKJL0021) 개별삭제
               PERFORM  S4000-KJL0021-PROCESS-RTN
                  THRU  S4000-KJL0021-PROCESS-EXT
           END-IF

      *@1 처리종료
